sense.gloss: statute of limitations, lapse of rights after a period of time, prescription (including acquisitive and extinctive prescription)
becoming invalid or void after a set time

sdata.j: この↑犯罪↑↓はんざい↓については|↑時効|↑↓じこう↓が↑成立↑↓せいりつ↓している。
sdata.e: The statute of limitations has already passed for this crime.
